@startuml
title Natural-Language Code Summary Execution Plan

skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName Noto Sans
skinparam packageStyle rectangle
skinparam ArrowColor #355C7D
skinparam PackageBorderColor #355C7D
skinparam PackageBackgroundColor #F7FBFF
skinparam RectangleBorderColor #355C7D
skinparam RectangleBackgroundColor #EEF6FF

rectangle "Phase 0\nBaseline Freeze" as P0
rectangle "Phase 1\nSummary Source Contract" as P1
rectangle "Phase 2\nImport-Time Summary Generation" as P2
rectangle "Phase 3\nRetrieval Integration" as P3
rectangle "Phase 4\nLive Fixture Proof Harness" as P4
rectangle "Phase 5\nE2E Proof Gate" as P5

P0 --> P1
P1 --> P2
P2 --> P3
P3 --> P4
P4 --> P5

note right of P0
API import로 clean fixture 생성
baseline domain-aware PM / RAG 결과 snapshot
end note

note right of P1
code_summary / symbol_summary source type
summary metadata / link contract
end note

note right of P2
workspace import/backfill 시
file/module/symbol summary 생성
knowledge_documents / chunks 저장
end note

note right of P3
hybrid retrieval 유지
role-aware summary weighting
PM preview knowledge fetch 반영
end note

note right of P4
baseline vs post-summary
same fixture / same scenarios
JSON diff report
end note

note right of P5
strict kernel burn-in
autonomy matrix
browser smoke
rag readiness with summary hits
domain-aware PM matrix pre/post proof
end note

@enduml
